{"tid":1417786,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【拆彈啊屌！】推到聽日民間記者會有哂重點！","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T01:50:49.000Z","uid":262207,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6ed48669f4ff3d5bfbf709fd3117253660ca1565","tid":1417786,"uid":262207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:10:52.000Z","msg":"係呀，我係P牌仔呀，唔驚就睇哂佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建議1：大point要強調首要資訊，方便攞sound bite。次要資訊留返大point後面解釋。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好話</span>「明明朝早高級警司記招話唔會針對記者<span style=\"color: green;\">（次要資訊）</span>，你夜晚就射記者個頭！<span style=\"color: red;\">（首要資訊）</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要講</span>「多區警察濫暴槍傷記者，令記者流血送院（<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首要資訊</span></span>）」，然後<span style=\"font-size: large;\">停頓</span>，再補充細節同次要資訊<br />\n<br />\n參考資料：<br />\n【8.5大罷工】多區記者遭警暴！催淚彈直射頭毁容流血 擊爆《蘋果》鏡頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190805&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59900268\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190805%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59900268&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BMwCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=7437ad21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190805%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59900268&h=86db869b\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190805&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59900268</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建議2：針對警黑暴力</span><br />\n<br />\n警察暴力、荃灣同北角黑社會暴力，係事實、大家有目共睹，就唔應該得我地自己見到。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果警犬記招有佢講，我地民間記招都必須爭奪譴責暴力的論述。</span><br />\n<br />\n參考資料：【8.5罷工集會●荃灣】7區集會5區出彈 兩黑衣男川龍街遭3名白衣男斬手腳踢心口<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190805&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59898572\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190805%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59898572&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BMwCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=6e280141\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190805%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59898572&h=41ed1953\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190805&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59898572</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建議3：道具好重要<br />\n<br />\n試下將明顯顯示出警察同黑社會暴力的畫面，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用A3 size彩印出嚟</span></span>。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">一個好的presentation入面，貼題的視覺元素同有組織的內容同樣重要</span></span><br />\n<br />\n參考資料：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ucdE0px.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FucdE0px.png&h=9e78fe6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">我知我P牌仔，講到呢到就算。大家踴躍啲建議聽日民間/連登仔記者會有咩重點，功德無量、一世平安呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"ab91c82afa9b4a970a54032127250b27d8d460f2","tid":1417786,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:11:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75fbaeefd1c4029659707ce5ee718574cf641080","tid":1417786,"uid":42079,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:16:26.000Z","msg":"唔該主力講兩點<br />\n1. 荃灣刀手著既衫同建制撐警既一樣<br />\n2. 懷疑警察特登引示威者去北角再加上預先挑起福建佬情緒引起兩派衝突"},{"pid":"90ff0703600ae1c0aaa5c57cf9b05ac5c5c156c3","tid":1417786,"uid":262207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:16:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命！</span>"},{"pid":"87ea07763a4747d20b3c6013145128028d520c7f","tid":1417786,"uid":262207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75fbaeefd1c4029659707ce5ee718574cf641080","tid":14177